{"tid":1159724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解香港人唔考慮去其他地方階級上流？","createTime":"2019-05-18T02:36:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-18T09:55:00.000Z","uid":20241,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"84947ce3cde2a8c9dac89207bd65819d1c42eed9","tid":1159724,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T02:36:59.000Z","msg":"如果你有層350呎私樓600萬免供<br />\n打份工兩三萬<br />\n冇乜其他資產<br />\n係香港最多就係中下產<br />\n手停口停<br />\n生個仔又入唔到名校<br />\n做到60歲好彩就叫做sm<br />\n咁就退休<br />\n過幾年發覺有病公立排28個月<br />\n去私家做啦份保單claim完呢次就冇左<br />\n過兩年復發要手術公立排4星期<br />\n一世人咁就玩完<br />\n<br />\n其實點解唔考慮去台灣，馬來西亞呢啲<br />\n層600萬私樓係個啲地方足夠你係城市買千呎新樓有剩遠小小買間鋪仔出租又好 或者筆錢做生意又好<br />\n搖身一變就做左地主階級<br />\n點解一係要留係香港一係就諗住歐美呢啲高難度地方呢"},{"pid":"cd6b39caaeff4e615ba69707e5b647b21a5196db","tid":1159724,"uid":88428,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T02:38:34.000Z","msg":"咁係下流定上流"},{"pid":"5a0d79a9b1d5f51881f5b0965224ee5aec30ffa6","tid":1159724,"uid":20241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cd6b39caaeff4e615ba69707e5b647b21a5196db","tid":1159724,"uid":88428,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T02:38:34.000Z","msg":"咁係下流定上流"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T02:43:01.000Z","msg":"唔知呀<br />\n去美國做倉同去馬拉收租<br />\n邊樣算高級啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be964670b2df2bbf8e464a78832a0fad3800343d","tid":1159724,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T02:44:20.000Z","msg":"留名想知"},{"pid":"85b2ff97a8de043f07472aecc96acebbad21b92d","tid":1159724,"uid":88428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a0d79a9b1d5f51881f5b0965224ee5aec30ffa6","tid":1159724,"uid":20241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cd6b39caaeff4e615ba69707e5b647b21a5196db","tid":1159724,"uid":88428,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T02:38:34.000Z","msg":"咁係下流定上流"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T02:43:01.000Z","msg":"唔知呀<br />\n去美國做倉